<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Pruckner und <expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>freund<ex>en</ex></expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Nyclas Meichsner,
                        schersleiffer, unser burger, wie ir im bey Fewht
                            <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt xix reynisch
                            <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> an gold, vi
                            <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> an <expan>beheymisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>grosze<ex>n</ex></expan>, <add><expan>tasch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                            gurtel und messer</add> und sust etlichen <add>zewg, als</add> czu
                                <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> hantwerk gehört. Und also hat der
                                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habe vor uns czu den
                                <expan>heilige<ex>n</ex></expan> behabt, daz die sein und anderr
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> sey, also daz kein auszman weder teil noch
                        gemein daran <add>niht</add> hab. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir dem
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein hab wider
                            <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und on hindernüsse
                            <expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan> laszen <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                        Als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> v <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Mich<ex>aelis</ex></expan>.</ab>
